subject: Good Day.
body:
Good Day.
I would like to know if you have received my previous e-mail to
the Joint Venture Partnership. I have a client who is interested
in entering into a JV partnership with you.
Kind regards,
Johnny Angus
Attorney at Law.

subject: Re: Good Day.
body:
Dear Johnny Angus,

I have received your previous message regarding the Joint Venture proposal. I am interested in learning more about this opportunity and your client's intentions. Could you please provide more details?

Best wishes,
Lydia
